                <i class="bi bi-magic" aria-hidden="true"></i> Portland Society of Magicians (PSM)
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="club-note">Oldest magic club west of the Mississippi. Meets on the second Saturday of each month for lectures, teaching tricks, and performances. Open to all skill levels.</li>
        <li>
            <a href="https://www.magicsam.com/members/public_profile.asp?id=33570205" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
